QuestData.Title: You Lift, Brul?
QuestData.Description: Do you even lift? If you can carry these weights to the statue of Liftbrul and back, maybe we can talk.
QuestData.LogDescription: Carry the weights to the statue of Liftbrul and return to Damrul the Stronk.
QuestData.RewardText: Stronger than you look, little one.
